data.description: Sprawling 4 bedroom 3 bathroom CBS pool home in Jupiter Farms. Enjoy your privacy on this 1.25 acre lot complete with detached garage and fenced backyard. The primary bedroom, located on the second floor has a stunning spa-like bathroom recently updated. Stacked bedroom upstairs with 1 bedroom and bathroom downstairs perfect for anyone looking for an in-law suite. The detached garage (28'x 40') has 14' ceilings with two 12' garage doors perfect for your RV or Boat. 2019 Metal roof, partial impact windows, 2021/2022 updates on flooring, kitchen, and bathrooms.
